data.description: This cozy home has everything you want and need! Upon arrival, you will be swept away by the open floorplan and gorgeous community of Whitehall Village with all of its amenities. The home offers a whole house generator, 4 bedrooms/ 3 full bathrooms in addition to a large bonus room upstairs and fenced in backyard. The master suite features tray ceilings, lots of closet space and a custom tile shower w/ bench seat. Very conveniently located between Kernersville/Winston areas, you will effortlessly find nearby highways, shopping & medical care. Don't miss out on this one and reserve your showing today!
